'''柯蒂斯·古德'''（{{lang-en|'''Curtis Good'''}}；{{bd|1993年|3月23日}}）是一位[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是後衛。現效力於[[澳洲職業足球聯賽|澳洲職業足球聯賽]]球隊[[墨爾本城|墨爾本城]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-au/news/4021/a-league/2012/07/25/3263727/work-permit-paves-way-for-curtis-good-to-complete-newcastle |title=Work permit paves way for Curtis Good to complete Newcastle United move |publisher=Goal.com |date=2012-07-25 |accessdate=2012-09-21 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502061729/http://www.goal.com/en-au/news/4021/a-league/2012/07/25/3263727/work-permit-paves-way-for-curtis-good-to-complete-newcastle |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20120731/its-good-news-for-magpies_2281670_2866556 |title=Newcastle United | News | Latest News | Latest News | It's Good News For Magpies |publisher=Newcastle United F.C |date= |accessdate=2012-09-21 |archive-date=2015-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213181146/http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20120731/its-good-news-for-magpies_2281670_2866556 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曾被紐卡斯爾外借至[[鄧迪聯足球俱樂部|鄧迪聯]]。他也代表[[澳大利亞國家足球隊|澳大利亞國家足球隊]]參賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20140514/good-named-in-socceroos-squad_2281670_3830903 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2015-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612101609/http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20140514/good-named-in-socceroos-squad_2281670_3830903 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

